headline: Evercore ISI Has In Line Rating on MetLife (MET)
summary: MetLife Inc. (NYSE:MET) is one of the 13 Deep Value Stocks to Buy Right Now. Evercore ISI analyst Thomas Gallagher, on February 11, slightly trimmed his target price on MetLife by 2.1% to $95 (from $97) but kept his In Line call on the stock.
